node.text: Introducing my new Porsche 911 Turbo S!! I honestly can’t believe this! I just want to say thank you to everyone who has watched and supported me over the years. I am truly so blessed for having all of y’all! Check out the new video if you wanna see more! And a lot more car vlogs/content to come! I love you guys!

node.text: Sometimes I use my beard to hide my flaws.. but today I’m going to be vulnerable and show you my flaws... my face! By partnering with @dollarshaveclub for their #MenGetReal campaign! I’ve always been insecure without facial hair and I know a lot of people who feel the same. But let’s get real men! Don’t hide anymore! Dollar Shave Club’s got all your grooming needs covered, now at a store near you! #ad #DollarShaveClub
